  "body": "<p>Got a little misty with this month's <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/galleries/81874-sydney-main-kit-only\">Main Kit only</a> layout at <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/shop/new?aff=6cc2c70f\">Studio Calico</a>, The add-on kits sold out really quick this time, and it's really no surprise. However there are some more <a href=\"http://bit.ly/YVwsBq\">Main kits left</a>. They were so much fun to work with. Here's how this page came together. I used white mist on the arrow mask that came in the main kit, <a href=\"http://bit.ly/YVwsBq\">Neverland</a>. I do my misting outside, sometimes on the porch, sometimes in a box on the porch.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"4a-DSC_0571-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600047754430-FN4Y4ZVZ1V6TPBLDK43B/4a-DSC_0571-600x398.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"4b-DSC_0573-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600047754337-M05EAP6HZ42QW5JCC3TE/4b-DSC_0573-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4c-DSC_0574-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600047754851-T7BK1MSZY9TCZRFVWTOT/4c-DSC_0574-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>I changed my mind several times as to how I wanted the page oriented.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"4d-DSC_0575-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600047789765-Z1KBP865Y0OW8E6ZEYY4/4d-DSC_0575-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4e-DSC_0576-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600047789636-UP3MEEY7XXVYA78JOF00/4e-DSC_0576-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4f-DSC_0577-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600047790518-SRWTAMZ6Q3RLT4604V8L/4f-DSC_0577-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4g-DSC_0578-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600047790405-VHIQL6R34K5V33265NRW/4g-DSC_0578-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4h-DSC_0579-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600047790944-3SKIAVD7ODI3VJ92L9IN/4h-DSC_0579-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4i-DSC_0580-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600047791082-IBCSSQR07RXW8VJ4KCYL/4i-DSC_0580-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4j-DSC_0581-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600047791604-4VV9NOOFHSBPGP97HOV3/4j-DSC_0581-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4k-DSC_0582-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600047791706-4XH6IZ75SHDUKGAVJ94O/4k-DSC_0582-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4l-DSC_0583-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600047846405-XW4JIV2DORTWYO7QHPJX/4l-DSC_0583-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4m-DSC_0584-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600047793133-IZNWBWQ6X8XCU5DMAUAF/4m-DSC_0584-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4n-DSC_0585-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600047877317-DXV89R099DTXZ9HQYO6I/4n-DSC_0585-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4o-sydney-562x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600047793246-XZCB5OJ02SK4DAJ3BO7I/4o-sydney-562x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Hope you enjoyed seeing the process! All the layouts using these amazing kits are in <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/creative-team-gallery/neverland/scrapbook/amy-tan--2?aff=6cc2c70f\">the gallery</a>. I'm also guest pinning for Studio Calico this week - you can see <a href=\"http://pinterest.com/studio_calico/amy-tan-for-sc-guest-pinner/\">the pinboard here</a>.</p>"
